                <h2>What You've Learned</h2>
                <div class="key-points">
                    <ul>
                        <li>‚úÖ <strong>Narrow AI</strong> is specialized for specific tasks (all AI today)</li>
                        <li>‚úÖ <strong>General AI</strong> would be flexible like humans (doesn't exist yet)</li>
                        <li>‚úÖ <strong>Supervised Learning</strong> learns from labeled examples</li>
                        <li>‚úÖ <strong>Unsupervised Learning</strong> discovers patterns in unlabeled data</li>
                        <li>‚úÖ <strong>Reinforcement Learning</strong> learns through trial, error, and rewards</li>
                        <li>‚úÖ Different problems require different AI approaches</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                
